{"tid":1805872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"江乙己筋條條綻出 “轉身不能算逃…待援！…警察的事，能算逃走麼？”","createTime":"2020-01-01T02:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T03:39:41.000Z","uid":105976,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abb287d4efd083892ba7713188e8275f8d256337","tid":1805872,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:08:44.000Z","msg":"江乙己一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道，&ldquo;江乙己，你伙記又柒出國際了！&rdquo;他不回答，對柜里說，&ldquo;責無旁貸，向前處理，化解危機不能逃走。&rdquo;便排出九文大錢。他們又故意的高聲嚷道，&ldquo;黑警死全家！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n江乙己睜大眼睛說，&ldquo;你怎麼這樣憑空污警察清白&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;什么清白？721我親眼見你們轉身逃走，市民被吊著打。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n江乙己便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道，&ldquo;轉身不能算逃&hellip;&hellip;待援！&hellip;&hellip;警察的事，能算逃走麼？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n接連便是難懂的話，什么&ldquo;交給上峰&rdquo;，什么&ldquo;拉闊&rdquo;之類，<br />\n引得眾人都哄笑起來：店內外充滿了快活的空气。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/2603862909734626/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnews.lancet%2Fvideos%2F2603862909734626%2F&d=WJuKoENqNSNgO%2FFXDb0as2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=1d6e0345\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/news.lancet/videos/2603862909734626/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n魯迅 《孔乙己》 最早發表在1919年4月    <br />\n100年前寫既劣根性 到而家都仲係好多人未改到"},{"pid":"75827deb6f42bbe07ddd6b60d274ae45938d34f8","tid":1805872,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"今日2點見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/81322272_2695522113828496_2043203289457098752_o.png?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_ohc=grauPpb0-IAAQmCTS-2lRb0dZxCKSgQ8nFKjF8VVgZL26f_R_yWB_-1Uw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=8ced170d038e5d35b20b13bf5acf196d&amp;oe=5EA63734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F81322272_2695522113828496_2043203289457098752_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_ohc%3DgrauPpb0-IAAQmCTS-2lRb0dZxCKSgQ8nFKjF8VVgZL26f_R_yWB_-1Uw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D8ced170d038e5d35b20b13bf5acf196d%26oe%3D5EA63734&h=9cdb1d31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11b8799cc61adbad45e4a19e6b208e7962421cb7","tid":1805872,"uid":81531,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"改返啲殘體字先再出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f2dacc19dbfd67872499ba9c8c7bdc1822281e","tid":1805872,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1be6c360291aae4571a0db8a64a66355df977bd3","tid":1805872,"uid":276415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"11b8799cc61adbad45e4a19e6b208e7962421cb7","tid":1805872,"uid":81531,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:15:52.000Z","msg":"改返啲殘體字先再出啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"曲直難分，講緊你"},{"pid":"b59d33c26057d8c53ed2dcbbf67fb44f072b0a79","tid":1805872,"uid":264387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"有一回對我說道，&ldquo;你讀過書么？&rdquo;我略略點一點頭。他說，&ldquo;讀過書，&hellip;&hellip;我便考你一考。觀星筆的星字，怎樣寫的？&rdquo;我想，狗一樣的人，也配考我么？便回過臉去，不再理會。肛穴己等了許久，很懇切的說道，&ldquo;不能寫罷？&hellip;&hellip;我教給你，記著！這些字應該記著。將來做律政司的時候，政治檢控要用。&rdquo;我暗想我和律政司的等級還很遠呢，而且我們政府也從不作政治檢控；又好笑，又不耐煩，懶懶的答他道，&ldquo;誰要你教，不是上面一個日下面一個生么？&rdquo;肛穴己顯出极高興的樣子，將兩個指頭的長指甲敲著柜台，點頭說，&ldquo;對呀對呀！&hellip;觀星筆有四樣寫法，你知道么？&rdquo;我愈不耐煩了，努著嘴走遠。肛穴己剛用指甲蘸了酒，在柜上寫鐳射槍激光炮，見我毫不熱心，便又歎一口气，顯出极惋惜的樣子。"},{"pid":"f8f07db172e4a48e2e3d51477fa36c199e08b57c","tid":1805872,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T02:41:57.000Z","msg":"<i